{"tid":833814,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[Netflix] 天盛長歌","createTime":"2018-09-23T18:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T10:57:30.000Z","uid":172513,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c1f553a874364ba88e86485aaca07c303d85b1","tid":833814,"uid":172513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T18:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/024510_5dcfecbabe22fd9a5e3683fa28df5531.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F024510_5dcfecbabe22fd9a5e3683fa28df5531.png&h=a3861db2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《天盛長歌》（英文：The Rise of Phoenixes），大任於公，天下承平。前名《凰權&middot;弈天下》，改編自天下歸元小說《凰權》，講述了天盛王朝逆境皇子寧弈和前朝皇族遺孤鳳知微之間步步為營，「弈一局權謀天下，博一場愛恨起伏」的宮廷權謀故事。電視劇由Netflix、華策克頓集團辛迪加影視、東申影業、好麥文化共同出品[3][4][5]，導演沈嚴、劉海波執導[6]，陳坤、倪妮、白敬亭、趙立新、倪大紅、袁弘、王鷗等主演[7]。<br />\n<br />\n該劇於2018年8月14日在湖南衛視金鷹獨播劇場首播[8]，並在芒果TV、愛奇藝每日22:00同步衛視播出。 Netflix將於2018年9月14日起, 在全球播放此劇。"},{"pid":"176cd1fdfb2dbe7acc999a6c2783544c0874b6ef","tid":833814,"uid":172513,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T18:46:20.000Z","msg":"全部七十集，值得細味欣賞。<br />\n<br />\nNetfilx出到30集 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73522a6f55677c035ab2613652ccf7c72c31a3b0","tid":833814,"uid":27616,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T20:00:58.000Z","msg":"我睇哂70集啦，應該係今年最好睇嘅大陸古裝劇"},{"pid":"3b7b9253608f0037d7c929534113b714ee1fe4a7","tid":833814,"uid":180515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T02:39:40.000Z","msg":"睇咗頭幾集，個女主點解明知周圍都有人搵緊佢，仲要離開王爺府?"},{"pid":"7b00e8eca1d4682136f9e230c132949c4c1d20b6","tid":833814,"uid":129288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T04:52:11.000Z","msg":"幾好睇 不過節奏太慢"},{"pid":"ba213cc08ab271bd518b09e9bcdfad33b309873d","tid":833814,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b7b9253608f0037d7c929534113b714ee1fe4